messageBody:
Don't?

If you want to test the superclass, then write tests for the
superclass. IMHO, there's nothing to test here.

In fact, I'm not even sure why you're implementing these methods. It
seems like not implementing them would have the same effect, unless
you're changing their visibility.

-Kevin
